flowchart TD
    title Chapter 17: Error Handling Strategies
    
    Start([Operation]) --> Result{Result~T,E~}
    
    Result -->|Ok| Success[Success Path]
    Result -->|Err| Handle{Handle Error}
    
    Handle --> Match[match statement]
    Handle --> IfLet[if let Err]
    Handle --> Question[? operator]
    Handle --> Unwrap[unwrap/expect]
    
    Match --> HandleErr[Handle gracefully]
    IfLet --> HandleErr
    Question --> Propagate[Propagate up]
    Unwrap --> Panic[Panic on error]
    
    HandleErr --> End([Continue])
    Propagate --> End
    Panic --> Crash([Crash])
    Success --> End
